text: Corbon, Calvados is a former commune. It is found in the Normandy region in the Calvados department in the northwest of France. On 1 January 2015, it was merged with the commune of Notre-Dame-d'Estrées to the new commune Notre- Dame-d'Estrées-Corbon. Category:Former communes in Calvados
title: Corbon, Calvados
